org.sonar.vary.plugin.xunit

Class TestResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sonar.vary.plugin.xunit.TestResource

  • public class TestResource
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a test resource in Sonar, i.e. a source code file which implements tests. Holds all testcases along with all measures collected from the reports.
